<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .alert-box {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .warning { color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>🔐 Account Recovery</h2>
    <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
    
    <div class="alert-box">
      <strong>Your account has been secured following a security alert.</strong><br><br>
      A request to change your email was detected and has been cancelled.
    </div>
    
    <div class="info-box">
      <strong>📋 Security Actions Taken:</strong><br>
      • All pending email changes cancelled<br>
      • All active sessions logged out<br>
      • Account temporarily locked<br>
      • Password reset required
    </div>
    
    <p><strong>📱 Request Details:</strong><br>
    Device: {{deviceInfo}}<br>
    IP Address: {{ipAddress}}<br>
    Time: {{requestTime}}</p>
    
    <p>Click the button below to reset your password and regain access to your account:</p>
    <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">🔑 Reset Password & Unlock Account</a>
    
    <p>Or use this recovery code: <strong>{{token}}</strong></p>
    
    <p class="warning">⚠️ This recovery link expires in 60 minutes.</p>
    
    <p>If you did not request this, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>{{appName}} Security Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>